PrecisAmendments to the PROHIBITED WEAPONS ORDER, NO. 11 which remove some variants of the "Benelli M1 Super 90" and the "Benelli M3 Super 90" shotguns from the list of prohibited weapons, add the "Interdynamics KG-99 Assault Pistol" to the list of weapon which must be surrendered, deactivated or exported, and establish a three-month amnesty period.
